# Google Apps Script Web App URL
# Follow the setup guide in ATHOPEN.md Section 6 to create the Google Sheet and
# deploy code.gs as a Web App, then paste the resulting /exec URL below.
#
# When set: the app reads players and matches from Google Sheets in real time —
#   roster changes and score updates in the sheet are immediately reflected on the site.
# When blank or missing: the app falls back to built-in mock data (no rebuild needed).
#
# Format:  https://script.google.com/macros/s/<YOUR_SCRIPT_ID>/exec
VITE_SHEETS_API_URL=
